# Dotfiles-managed — replaces Cursor's generated git-sync block.
# ~/.cursor is symlinked to this directory; Cursor writes a broad
# git-sync .gitignore here to track its own runtime state, but we only
# want to track the plugin source (cursor/plugins/local/cheese-grok/).
# Everything else (commands/, rules/, skills/, skills-cursor/, projects/,
# etc.) is either a deploy artifact (source already in plugins/) or
# Cursor IDE runtime cache — none of it belongs in version control.
*
!.gitignore
!plugins/
!plugins/**
